# Brammo Admin (CakePHP 5 plugin)

- Namespace `Brammo\Admin\`; plugin name `Brammo/Admin`; routes prefix `/admin`.
- `declare(strict_types=1);` on every PHP file; type-hint parameters and returns.
- User strings: `__d('brammo/admin', '...')` — update `resources/locales/` when adding UI text.
- Templates/elements: `Brammo/Admin.*` (e.g. `Brammo/Admin.Form/image`). Assets: `Brammo/Admin.{css,js}` in `webroot/`.
- Config: `Configure::read('Admin.*')` from `config/admin.php`; document new keys in `docs/CONFIGURATION.md`.
- Depends on `brammo/auth` (auto-loaded). Controllers extend `AppController` → `AppView` + Authentication.

Before finishing: `composer check` (tests, PHPCS, PHPStan on `src/`). Use `composer check-full` for Psalm.

File manager logic lives in `src/FileManager/FileManagerService.php`; keep HTTP/flash/JSON in the controller.

File manager: preserve `isValidFolder`, `sanitizeFilename`, `isPathWithinBase` — no path traversal regressions.

Keep diffs small; follow patterns in existing helpers/controllers/tests.
